name: Things I did before I left

metadata.name: i can't think about myself anymore
metadata.description:
Why?
Why does this thing inside me never go away?

Sometimes alone at night, I talk to death and it tries to give me a solution to all this.

What are my reasons for continuing? I'm not the same anymore
